description:
A beaver causes a flood into Tony Beets’s only gold-producing cut, leaving his team scrambling. Meanwhile, Kevin Beets learns that Parker Schnabel is poaching another member of his crew, Rick Ness leases ground from Troy Taylor, and Parker gets Sluicifer firing up again on the Golden Mile, gunning for a record-breaking season.

#GoldRush new Fridays at 8P on Discovery.

#Discovery #GoldRush

About Gold Rush
Motivated by a depressed economy, hard-working gold miners get to work both in America and across the globe in an attempt to strike it rich.
